answers.body_markdown:
we fix the issue by creating a new spark sql dialect

    import org.apache.spark.sql.jdbc.JdbcDialect
    
    object MariaDBDialect extends JdbcDialect {
      override def quoteIdentifier(colName: String): String = colName
    
      override def canHandle(url: String): Boolean = url.startsWith(&quot;jdbc:mariadb&quot;)
    }

before reading your mariadb dataframe just call 

    import org.apache.spark.sql.jdbc.JdbcDialects
    // register specific dialect for mariaDB as it isn&#39;t implemented in spark
    JdbcDialects.registerDialect(MariaDBDialect)

