When converting between strings and byte arrays, you are using some encoding mechanism. If you don&#39;t specify it, it will use the default encoding for your platform. In your case, it seems to be UTF-8 because some characters are encoded on 3 bytes.
With the ISO-8859-1 encoding, each character is encoded as a single byte. Try using it instead:

